I '''Niels Henrik David Bohr''' ({{IPA-da|ˈnels ˈboɐ̯ˀ}}; 7 Octubre 1885&nbsp;– 18 Noviembre 1962)<ref name="nobelprize.org" /> metung yang [[physicist]] ibat [[Denmark]] a minambag king pamitátag ning pangabalangkas ning atomo ampo king pamanintindi king pangabalangkas ning atomo ampo king [[quantum mechanics]], at para kaniti, tinggap ne ing  [[Nobel Prize in Physics]] anyang 1922.<ref name="frs">{{cite doi|10.1098/rsbm.1963.0002}}</ref> Ayalkus (''developed'') ne ing modelu ning atomo nung nu ing nucleus atyu king libutad at dudurut la reng electron king orbit padurut kaniti, a kinumpara na kareng planetang dudurut king aldo. Penigobran ne ing idea king quantum mechanics a deng electron mumukyat la manibat king metung a energy level paras keng tutuki kareng malinong takbang to another in (''discrete steps'') at e taglus-taglus o alang angganan king pilatan. , not (''continuously''). Tiru nalang Bohr, at mekiugnayan ya kareng dakal kareng manimunang physicist ning dilanwa/siglu king kayang [[Niels Bohr Institute|institute]] king [[Copenhagen]]. Kayabe ya king grupu da reng British physicist a manigobra king [[Manhattan Project]]. Pepakasalan neng Bohr i Margrethe Nørlund kanitang 1912, at ing metung kareng karelang ának, i [[Aage Bohr]], physicist ya naman, at anyang 1975 tinggap ne ing Nobel Prize. 

